{"tid":513692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多謝泛民] 林鄭月娥指遊行人數減　對社會趨平靜感鼓舞","createTime":"2017-12-29T20:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T01:38:16.000Z","uid":59491,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5dd966197697f927435a8f3832f43e61492f1d","tid":513692,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T20:18:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥接受本台專訪時說，上任近半年，社會平穩了，爭吵聲音小了，仍然有集會示威，但參與人數減少，感覺是香港社會平靜下來，但究竟是本屆政府功勞，還是香港人感疲累，只想平靜開心，很難說清楚，但政府是感到鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政府早前沒向立法會提交《印花稅修訂條例草案》等法案，令修改議事規則速戰速決，會否令人感到是乘人之危；林鄭月娥說，她自己觀察，沒有這感覺，又強調政府提交到立法會的議程，要審時度勢，如果明知提甚麼議案也成為被拉布對象，只會「搵來搞」，眼見議員就一些無關痛癢、很簡單的附屬法例，也要討論，在如此局面，政府有所應對，理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1371546-20171223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1371546-20171223.htm&d=NKIhMwSmdKvAVKj3YKoWrdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d9f4e8f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1371546-20171223.htm&h=a3471afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1371546-20171223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"249b8ea9ff770b26a032eb945a7e99ac6042a49f","tid":513692,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T21:10:44.000Z","msg":"咁本土派吹雞遊行應該好多人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ba528831bd151d943f381763a1fb890a420e92","tid":513692,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T23:10:44.000Z","msg":"多謝班成日今天我既口中勇武派。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/